                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">City policeman</hi>. 566). I took the prisoner, searched him at the station, and found on him a half crown, a shilling, a sixpence, a halfpenny, a ring, three watches, a knife, a tobacco pipe, and a key (<hi rend="italic">pro<lb></lb>duced</hi>)—he said that it was not him, it was a man who was passing by.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner's Defence</hi>. I was coming from the India House, and the man took hold of me; there were a great many people on the pavement; a person behind me threw them down.</p>
